name: Your body is
description:
A collaboration with Sudowrite. Entranced with the idea of handwritten AI love notes.

Full poem:

everything you aspire
to be, you are right now;
go on, take a look.

your body is a bouquet
of every flower ever grown.

your heart is the rhythm of the ocean.
your mind is a million questions

and your mouth is a river,
a river that will take you to the ocean.
